 At Equinix, we spark new opportunities by making internet better and enabling businesses to deploy and scale their digital infrastructure where everything is within reach.
 We offer the world's largest platform of high-quality data centers, including reliable interconnection to ecosystems of enterprises, clouds, networks and IT providers.
 With our global footprint of 200+ data centers spanning 53 metros in 5 continents, we currently serve nearly 10,000 customers, including the largest cloud providers, Fortune 500 enterprises and Global 2000 companies. Platform Equinix contains the highest share of public cloud on-ramps and most physically- and virtually-interconnected ecosystems.
 Our culture is at the heart of our success and it is our authentic, humble, gritty people who build The Magic of Equinix. We share a real passion for winning and put the customer at the center of everything we do.
 We are also big on innovation and constantly look for ways to bring to bear technology to better serve the evolving needs of our customers and benefit society in an increasingly digital world.
